content: I'll definitely consider those recommendations. I've been trying out some chairs at the office supply store, but I haven't had a chance to read up on them too much. By the way, I also recently rearranged my living room to make space for my new elliptical machine, and I ended up with a really comfortable reading nook with the armchair I inherited from my parents. Do you have any suggestions for some good books to read while I'm on my elliptical?
